# Objetivo / Target: Bloquear tentativas de buffer overflow remoto / Block remote buffer overflows attempts.

<rule>
ip dst(servers)
tcp dst(1-1023)
tcp nocase(|90 90 90 90 90 90 90 90 90 90 90 90 90 90 90 90 90 90 90 90 90 90 90 90 90 90 90 90 90 90|)
message=(bufferoverflow-1) Envio de NOP / NOP send
action=action1
</rule>

<rule>
ip dst(servers)
udp dst(1-1023)
udp nocase(|90 90 90 90 90 90 90 90 90 90 90 90 90 90 90 90 90 90 90 90 90 90 90 90 90 90 90 90 90 90|)
message=(bufferoverflow-2) Envio de NOP / NOP send
action=action1
</rule>
